source.description:
Twilio-compatible enum. VoiceML production emits only
`OutboundAPI`, `StartCallRecordingAPI`, and `Conference`;
the other values are declared for SDK compatibility.

post.description:
Creates a Voice v1 IpRecord (a standalone allowed source IP) for
the authenticated account. `IpAddress` is required;
`CidrPrefixLength` defaults to 32 (a single host).
